description:
List of San Francisco Department of Public Health clinics offering flu vaccinations throughout the city in fall 2013.

This dataset complies with the  emerging Data Specification for Flu Shot Locations. For information about the 
specification, please see https://github.com/CityOfPhiladelphia/flu-shot-spec.

For more information about SFDPH's Influenza Program  www.sfcdcp.org/flu or call 311


For more information about SFDPH's Open data Initiatives 
http://www.sfphes.org/resources/health-data or Contact Cyndy.comerford@sfdph.org
